Package net.sourceforge.jasa.market.auctioneer

Interface Summary
Auctioneer Classes implementing this interface define the rules for matching orders in the marketplace and producing the resulting transaction set.
 

Class Summary
AbstractAuctioneer An abstract class representing an auctioneer managing shouts in an market.
AscendingAuctioneer Auctioneer for standard multi-unit english ascending market.
ClearingHouseAuctioneer An auctioneer for a clearing house market.
ContinuousDoubleAuctioneer An auctioneer for a double-market with continuous clearing.
ContinuousDoubleAuctioneerEE Deprecated. GenericDoubleAuctioneer with EquilibriumBeatingAcceptingPolicy should be used.
GenericAuctioneer An modular auctioneer for a double market.
PeriodicClearingHouseAuctioneer Deprecated.
